[SHORT DESC]
10% chance to confuse opponent. 

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Deals damage and has a 10% chance to confuse the target.</p>

<h2>Competitive Use</h2>
<p>Confusion is the weakest special Psychic-type move available, and with the existence of Psychic as a more powerful version, more easily available option, there is literally no reason to use Confusion in a competitive environment.</p>

<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/bw/moves/psychic">Psychic</a> is a stronger alternative with 90 Base Power.</p>
<p><a href="/bw/moves/psyshock">Psyshock</a> is an alternative with 80 Base Power that deals physical damage.</p>